whatCanDoTitle: What can I do on Petown?
whatIsPetown: Petown is a pet care app where you can take care of and understand your pet completely.
whatCanDo: Coming to Petown, you can shop for accessories, food, clothes, ... and book spa, hotel, veterinary for your pets. Also, you can interact with people with similar interests through a magazine for pet. Moreover, Petown provides great tools such as Pet Scan, Pet Love, Pet Wiki for you to enjoy a happy life with your Pet.
animalServe: Petown's vision is to build a town for all animals that are human pets. For now, dogs and cats are our main subject. We will expand to offer a wide variety of animals and provide you with the best possible experiences.
scanTour: You can check your pet breed here!
crushTour: Find crush for your pet and for you here!
addTour: Add your pet and start enjoying!!!
